《'''Christmas Saves the Year'''》是美国音乐组合Twenty One Pilots创作并录制的一首圣诞单曲。于2020年12月8日，在COVID-19大流行期间通过Fueled by Ramen发布，歌曲表达了即使在动荡的一年中，仍然可以在圣诞节找到乐观的想法。<ref name=":0">{{Cite web|title=Hear twenty one pilots’ surprise holiday song "Christmas Saves The Year"|url=https://www.altpress.com/news/twenty-one-pilots-christmas-saves-the-year-song/|accessdate=December 9, 2020|author=Campbell|date=December 9, 2020|first=Rachel|work=Alternative Press|language=en-US|archive-date=2020-12-09|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201209020322/https://www.altpress.com/news/twenty-one-pilots-christmas-saves-the-year-song/|dead-url=no}}</ref>

== 背景 ==
《Christmas Saves the Year》是在主唱Tyler Joseph的家庭工作室里创作和录制的。<ref>{{Cite web|title=Twenty One Pilots release holiday single, 'Christmas Saves The Year' | NME|url=https://www.nme.com/en_asia/news/music/twenty-one-pilots-release-holiday-single-christmas-saves-the-year-2834864|accessdate=December 9, 2020|date=December 9, 2020|work=NME | Music, Film, TV, Gaming & Pop Culture News|language=en|archive-date=2020-12-31|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201231030917/https://www.nme.com/en_asia/news/music/twenty-one-pilots-release-holiday-single-christmas-saves-the-year-2834864|dead-url=no}}</ref>Twenty One Pilots在主唱Tyler Joseph参加[[奇波雷墨西哥燒烤|奇波雷]]挑戰者[[堡垒之夜|堡垒之夜]]系列赛为[[願望成真基金|願望成真基金]]筹款的[[Twitch|Twitch]]直播结束后<ref name=":0"/><ref>{{Cite web|title=Chipotle Challenger Series 2020: Everything You Need to Know|url=https://www.dexerto.com/sponsored/chipotle-challenger-series-2020-everything-you-need-to-know-1286259/|accessdate=December 9, 2020|date=December 4, 2020|work=Dexerto|language=en|archive-date=2021-01-28|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210128061448/https://www.dexerto.com/sponsored/chipotle-challenger-series-2020-everything-you-need-to-know-1286259/|dead-url=no}}</ref>首次公开了这首歌曲，此前他曾在直播中为观众预告了“一份礼物”。<ref>{{Cite tweet|user=twentyonepilots|number=1336497936658731010|date=December 9, 2020|title=an original twenty one pilots christmas song written and recorded in tyler's home studio. from us to you, merry christmas}}</ref><ref>{{Cite web|title=See why fans think new music from twenty one pilots is arriving soon|url=https://www.altpress.com/news/twenty-one-pilots-new-music-fan-theories/|accessdate=December 9, 2020|author=Dowd|date=December 8, 2020|first=Rachael|work=Alternative Press|language=en-US|archive-date=2021-01-28|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210128121840/https://www.altpress.com/news/twenty-one-pilots-new-music-fan-theories/|dead-url=no}}</ref>

最初不愿写圣诞节歌的约瑟夫因“通过一个小女孩的视角体验圣诞节”受到启发。曲目的声音受到一种叫{{Translink|en|Mellotron|美乐特朗}}的乐器的启发。<ref name=":1">{{Cite web|title=Tyler Joseph Interview with Zane Lowe - CSTY (12.9.20) - YouTube|url=https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=alJ7K-_EP38&t=624s|accessdate=December 28, 2020|work=www.youtube.com|archive-date=2021-01-28|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210128060343/https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=alJ7K-_EP38&t=624s|dead-url=no}}</ref>

== 音樂 ==
约瑟夫从他“住在一些大城市的小公寓的朋友”的角度写了这首歌，他們“正在权衡今年是否应该见家人的选择”。<ref name=":1"/>

== 音乐影片 ==
直播结束后，歌曲在各音樂流播平台上線，一支可视化器影片在[[YouTube|YouTube上]]放映。该影片由Johnny Chew导演和制作动画。<ref>{{Cite web|title=Twenty One Pilots share festive new single 'Christmas Saves The Year'|url=https://www.hotpress.com/music/twenty-one-pilots-share-festive-new-single-christmas-saves-the-year-22835758|accessdate=December 13, 2020|author=Brayden|first=Kate|work=Hotpress|archive-date=2020-12-10|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201210142706/https://www.hotpress.com/music/twenty-one-pilots-share-festive-new-single-christmas-saves-the-year-22835758|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{Cite web|title=Twenty One Pilots Release Holiday Single|url=https://vermilioncountyfirst.com/2020/12/09/twenty-one-pilots-release-holiday-single/|accessdate=December 13, 2020|author=News|first=Music|work=Vermilion County First}}</ref>

